</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>What if I don’t know my student’s bus number?</h3>
  <p>The staff of the BPS Transportation Hotline can tell you what your student’s bus number is.  The BPS Transportation Hotline is at (617) 635-9520.  The hotline is available Monday through Friday: 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>How many buses can I sign up to track?</h3>
  <p>This application is a service only for the immediate guardians of BPS parents.  You will be able to track all of the buses assigned to the students for whom you are the guardian, but only those buses.</p>
</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>Who else can see what bus numbers I signed up for?</h3>
  <p>BPS Transportation Staff are the only people that can see that information.  Your name, password and bus numbers associated with your account are otherwise private and will not be shared.</p>
</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>What if my student’s bus or bus number changes either permanently or for a particular day?</h3>
  <p>If your student will be taking a different bus to or from school on a permanent basis, simply call the Transportation Hotline at (617) 635-9520 and ask for them to change the bus you can see in this application.  The hotline is available Monday through Friday: 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
  <p>If your student will riding a different bus for just one day, we will be unable to update the change for that day to allow you to track the new bus.</p>
</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>What if I forget my password?</h3>
  <p>You can reset your password by going to the “Sign-In” page on the application and clicking “Forgot your password?”</p>
  <p>Alternatively, you can call the BPS Transportation Hotline at (617) 635-9520, who can delete and recreate your account.  The hotline is available Monday through Friday: 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
</div>
<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
  <h3>Do I have to sign up each year?</h3>
  <p>Yes.  At the beginning of every school year, you will have to sign up again, by calling the BPS Transportation Hotline. The BPS Transportation Hotline is at (617) 635-9520.  The hotline is available Monday through Friday: 8:30 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.</p>
</div>
